text: The 2016 Antrim Senior Hurling Championship was the 116th staging of the Antrim Senior Hurling Championship since its establishment by the Antrim County Board in 1901. The championship began on 7 August 2016 ended on 25 September 2016. ==Preliminary Match== ==Quarter-Finals== ==Semi-Finals== ==Final== ==External links== * Antrim GAA website ==References== Antrim Senior Hurling Championship Category:Antrim Senior Hurling Championship
